quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"Simoore, Men jippinii nde Men farlii nde, Men jippini e nder mayre Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe belajo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jeenoowo on foccee gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe paatawol(looci) teemedere, wata yurmeende ma…ď…ďe nanngu on e fii Diina Alla kan, si tawii on laatike hi…óon gom…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol …ďe ngol jamaa immorde e gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jeenoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resatah mo si wanaa gorko jinoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, …óum harminaama e dow gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  24,4,"E …ďen …ďe no tukka rew…ďe saŇčii…ďe …ďen refti hara …ďe addaali seedee…ďe nayo, haray piyee …ďe paatawol(looci) cappan…óe jeetati. Wata on ja…ďan …ďe seedagol poomaa. ∆Āen …óon, ko kam…ďe woni Faasiqii…ďe …ďen"
  24,5,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,6,"E …ďen …ďe no tukka sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen hara laatanaaki …ďe seedee…ďe si wanaa wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko yo go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kanko ko e goongu…ďe …ďen o jeyaa"
  24,7,"Jowa…ďun …óum, wonndema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ďe …ďen"
  24,8,"∆Āe dunyira e [sonnaajo on] lepte …óen, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenoo…ďe …ďen o jeyaa"
  24,9,"Jowa…ďun …óum, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e goongu…ďe …ďen o jeyaa"
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonndema Alla ko O ja…ďoowo tuubuubuye √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  24,11,"Pellet, …ďen addu…ďe penaale …óen ko …ďe jamaa jeyaa…óo e moo…óon, wata on sikku …óum ko bone mo'on; ko woni …óum ko mo∆ī∆īere mo'on. No woodani kala ne…ó…óo immorde e ma…ď…ďe ko o faggitii kon e junuubu, on fawtii…óo maw…óum [junuubu on] immorde e ma…ď…ďe, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe"
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde nanu…óon …óum, wor…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen e rew…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen …ďe yananee ka wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi, …ďe wi'a: \"∆äum ko penaale …ďanngu…óe nii"
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde …ďe addata e …óum seedee…ďe nayo, si …ďe addaali seedee…ďe …ďen; haray …ďen …óon, ka Alla ko kam…ďe woni fenoo…ďe …ďen"
  24,14,Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e Yurmeende Makko nden e dow moo…óon ka aduna e ka laakara Lepte maw…óe meemayno on fii kon ko ukki…óon e muu…óum
  24,15,"Tuma nde werlorayno…óon …óum …óenn…óe moo…óon, wowliron kunndu…óe moo…óon kon ko ganndal alanah on e muu…óum sikkon …óum kadi ko newii…óum, hara non …óum ko mawnu…óom ka Alla"
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanu…óon nde, wi'on: \"Haanaa men nde men wowlata e dum, Senayee woodanii Ma, …óum ko fenaande mawnde nii"
  24,17,"Alla no waajaade on fii wata on fillo sugu [ndee fenaande] poomaa, si tawii on laatike gom…óin…ďe"
  24,18,Alla no …ďannginannde on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo
  24,19,"Pellet, …ďen yi…óu…ďe yo bone …óen saako e [hoore] …ďen gom…óin…ďe; no woodani …ďe Lepte muusu…óe ka aduna e ka Laakara. Alla no Anndi, onon on anndah"
  24,20,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden e tawde pellet, Alla ko O Newii…óo Hinndotooao"
  24,21,"Ko onon …ďen gom…óin…ďe, wata on jokku …óate Seytaane …óen, kala jokku…óo …óate Seytaane …óen, pellet, o yamiray [mo] ko boni kon e ko a√Īaa kon. Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e moo…óon laa…ďataano poomaa, kono Alla hiMo la…ď…ďina on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,22,"Wata joomiraa…ďe …ďural ngal e yaajeende nden e moo…óon woondu wonndema …ďe okkortaa …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen e …ďillii…ďe …ďen e feru…ďe …ďen ka Laawol Alla, yo …ďe yaafo. Kaa on yi…óaa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko O Yawtoowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,23,"Pellet, …ďen wonu…ďe tukkude [sonnaa…ďe] saŇčii…ďe welsindii…ďe gom…óin…ďe, …ďe hu…óaama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani …ďe Lepte maw…óe"
  24,24,"√Ďalnde seedoytoo e dow ma…ď…ďe …óen…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko …ďe laatinoo kon hi…ďe golla"
  24,25,"Nden √Ďalnde Alla huu…ďinanay …ďe [njo…ďdi] Diina ma…ď…ďe Goongaha kan, …ďe annda pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga ∆Āannguka kan"
  24,26,"Rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen, wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen. ∆Āee …óoo ko hisnaa…ďe e kon ko …ďe wowlata, no woodani …ďe haforaneede e arsike teddu…óo"
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe, wata on naatu e cuu…ói tanaa cuu…ói mo'on …óin haa duŇčino…óon salminon e dow yim…ďe majji …ďen, ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on. Bela jo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,28,"Si on tawaali nder ton go…ó…óo, wata on naatu ton haa duŇčane…óon, si on wi'aama: \"Yiltee\" haray yiltee, ko …óum …ďuri laa…ďannde on. Alla non hiMo Anndi ko golloton kon"
  24,29,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde naatoton e cuu…ói …ói ho…óiraaka hara no e nder majji miranhoy mo'on, Alla non hiMo Anndi ko won…óon e fe√Ī√Īinde e ko won…óon e suu…óude"
  24,30,"Maakan wor…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe heltu ndar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe reena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko …óum …ďurata la…ď…ďinnde …ďe. Pellet, Alla ko O Humpitii…óo ko …ďe huuwata"
  24,31,"Maakan rew…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe heltu ndar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe reena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, wata …ďe fe√Ī√Īin cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin si wanaa ko fee√Īi kon e mayri. Yo …ďe fawu tiggaaje ma…ď…ďe …óen ka becce ma…ď…ďe, wata …ďe fe√Ī√Īinan cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin si wanaa genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maa…óum baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum baabiraa…ďe genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe banndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďen …ďe …ďe jeyiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe maa…óum …ďen wor…ďe jokkoo…ďe …ďe haaju mun alaa e rew…ďe, maa…óum boobo mo ∆īellitaaki e awraaji sonnaa…ďe …ďen. Wata …ďe tappindir koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen fii yo Annde ko …ďe suu…ói kon immorde e cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe. Tuubee rutto…óon ka Alla on fow mo'on, ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe bela jo'o on malete"
  24,32,"Resinee …ďe resaali …ďen e moo…óon e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen immorde e muccu…ďe moo…óon e hor…ďe moo…óon, si …ďe laatike waasu…ďe Alla al…óinay …ďe immorde e ∆Āural Makko ngal, Alla ko O Yaaju…óo Anndu…óo"
  24,33,"∆Āe he…ďaali feere resugol …ďen yo …ďe habbo haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural Makko ngal. ∆Āen wonu…ďe …óa…ď…ďude soottaade e …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, soottaadede …ďe si on anndii e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, jonnee …ďe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wata on waawnu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e fii jeeno, si …ďe faandike saŇčaade, wata on …óa…ď…ďu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ďe pellet, Alla …ďaawo baawnugol …ďe ko O Surroowo Yurmitee…óo"
  24,34,"Gom…óii Men jippinii e moo…óon Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe e misal immorde e …ďeya wulinoo…ďe ko adii on e waaju wonannde huloo…ďe [Alla] …ďen"
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni Ndaygu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sifa Ndaygu Makko ngun ko wano tu…ó…óere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e nder biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde hu…ď…ďa immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyankowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyankowal nebban maggal …óan no …ďadoo jalbude, hay si yiite meemaali …óan, ndaygu e hoore ndaygu, Alla no fewnira ndaygu Makko ngun on mo O Muuyi, Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected"
  24,36,E nder cuu…ói …ói Alla duŇčii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde Makko jantee e nder majji Subunhinanee Mo nder majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe
  24,37,"Wor…ďe …ďe njulaaku e ngeyngu maapintaa …óum gaayi jaŇčtagol Alla e √Īimnugol Julde nden e tottu- gol Jakka on, hi…ďe huli √Ďalaande nde waylitoytoo e muu…óum …ďer…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen"
  24,38,"Fii yo Alla yo…ďoy…ďe ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko …ďe gollunoo kon, O …ďeydana …ďe e ∆Āural Makko ngal. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko Aldaa hasboore"
  24,39,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen no wa'i wa merere wonunde e boowal, …óon…óaa…óo on no sikka ko nde ndiyam, haa si o arii e mayre o tawataa hay e huunde, o tawa Alla ka Makko O huu…ďinana mo hasboore makko nden, Alla ko O Yaawu…óo Hasboore. @Corrected"
  24,40,"Maa…óum ko wano ni…ďe e maayo luggungo, no suddi ngo benpe∆ī∆īe no dow maggo benpe∆ī∆īe no dow majje duule, ni…ďe yoga e majje no e dow yoga, si o yaltinii junngo makko ngon o …ďadotaako yi'ugol ngo. On mo Alla wa…óanaali ndaygu hara o alaa ndaygu"
  24,41,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla no subuhinanaade Mo …ďen wonu…ďe ka kammuuli e ka leydi e colli …óin kadi ko saffinii…ói? Gooto kala e …óii gom…óii anndii julde mu'un nden e subuhinaali mu'un …óin, Alla ko O Anndu…óo ko …ďe Huuwata"
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, ko faade ka Alla woni wa…ótinirde nden"
  24,43,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira nde, refti O wa…óa nde fawondirnde hi…óa yi'a to…ďo ngon no yalta e nder mayre, ngo jippoo immorde ka kammu, immorde e pelle no e nder mayre marmalle hiMo hewtina …óe on mo O Muuyi, hiMo pottina …óe on mo O Muuyi? Ndaneeri ma∆īe mayre no do'a na…ďude gii…óe …óen"
  24,44,"Alla hiMo waylita jemma on e √Īalorma on, pellet, na wonii e …óum tasakuyee wonannde joomiraa…ďe gii…óe …ďen"
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala daabe hun immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muu…óum, no e majji yaarooji koy…óe muu…óm no e majji kadi yaarooji [koy…óe] nayi. Alla hiMo Taga ko O Muuyi, pellet, Alla ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  24,46,"Gom…óii Men jippinii Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe, Alla no fewna on mo O muuyii faade e Laawol foccii ngol"
  24,47,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii Alla e Nulaa…óo on, men …óoftike, refti huccita fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďaawo …óum, …ďen wonaali gom…óin…ďe"
  24,48,"Si …ďe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, tawa fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe"
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kam…ďe mari goonga kan, …ďe aray ka makko ko …ďe …óoftii…ďe"
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, kaa …ďe sikkiti, kaa …ďe hulu wata Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on too√Īu …ďe? Ko woni, …ďee ko kam…ďe woni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol gom…óin…ďe …ďen si …ďe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ko nde …ďe wi'ata: \"Men nanii men …óoftike.\" ∆Āen …óon ko kam…ďe woni malaa…ďe …ďen"
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on o huli Alla o rentii [e Lepte Makko …óen] haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni malaa…ďe …ďen"
  24,53,"∆Āe woondiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje ma…ď…ďe, si a yamirii …ďe ma …ďe yaltu sanne. Maaku: \"wata on woondu, …óoftaare no anndaa, pellet, Alla ko humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  24,54,"Maaku: \"∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on\". Si …ďe huccitii(runtiima) anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko roonda …óon kon, si on …óoftike mo on feeway, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ďanngungol"
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gom…óin…ďe e moo…óon …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin O lontinay …ďe ka leydi wano O lontinirnoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ma O wee…ďinan …ďe diina ma…ď…ďe ka O welanaa …ďe, ma O wattitan …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ďe rewam wata …ďe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ďaawo …óum haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni faasiqii…ďe …ďen"
  24,56,"√Ďii…ďee e Julde totton Jakka on …óofto…óon kadi Nulaa…óo on, bela jo'o on Yurmete"
  24,57,"Wata a sikku …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde"
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe, yo sakkintino e moo…óon …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, e …ďen …ďe yottaaki koy…óol immorde e moo…óon, laabi tati ko adii Julde Peeral nden, e tuma wallinton conci moo…óon ka njolloro e ka …ďaawo Julde gee∆īe ko awraaji moo…óon tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki …ďe …ďaawo majji, jinndoo…ďe hakkunde moo…óon, yoga e moo…óon e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla …ďanngini- rani on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  24,59,"Si sukaa…ďe moo…óon yottike kellefuyee, yo …ďe sakkitinono wano duŇčinornoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ko wano nii Alla …ďannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  24,60,"E sonnaa…ďe jottii…ďe …ďen, …ďen …ďe jortaaki desal bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe nde …ďe wallinta conci ma…ď…ďe …óin hara …ďe wonaa fe√Ī√Īin…ďe cu…óaari, ko nde …ďe nantotoo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďe, Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,61,"Bakkaatu fawaaki bun…óu on, bakkaatu fawaaki la∆īu…óo on, bakkaatu fawaaki nawnu…óo on, fawaaki e wonkiiji moo…óon nde √Īaamoton ka cuu…ói moo…óon maa…óum ka cuu…ói baabiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói musi…ó…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói banndiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói bappiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói yaayiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óom ka cuu…ói kaawiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ďe moo…óon ka dewol, maa…óum …óin …ói jogi…óon cottir…óe muu…óum, maa…óum gi…óo moo…óon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde hawtoton √Īaamon maa…óum √Īaamon ko on sertu…ďe. Si on naatay e cuu…ói salminee e dow wonkiiji moo…óon, hiwraango immorde ka Alla barkinaango laa…ďungo, ko wano nii Alla …ďannguniranta on Aayeeje …óen belajo'o onon on haqqilay"
  24,62,"Anndu gom…óin…ďe …ďen ko …ďen gom…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftu…óo, …ďe yahatah haa …ďe duŇčinoo e makko, pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiray…ďe ma duŇčayee ko …ďen …óon woni gom…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake ma…ď…ďe, duŇčano on mo yi…óu…óaa [duŇčanaade] e ma…ď…ďe, insinano…óaa …ďe ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,63,"Wata on wa…óu noddugol Nulaa…óo on hakkunde moo…óon wano noddugol yoga e moo…óon yoga. Gom…óii Alla no Anndi …ďen sortotoo…ďe e moo…óon e moltagol, …ďen wonu…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo …ďe rento fii wata fitina hi…ďu …ďe maa…óum Lempte muusu…óe he…ďa …ďe"
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gom…óii hiMo Anndi ko wonu…óon e hoore mu'un kon, √Ďalnde …ďe ruttetee faade ka Makko O yeetoo …ďe ko …ďe gollunoo kon. Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"